title: Secret Wars I & II
description:
Marvel Super Heroes Secret Wars is a twelve-issue comic book limited series published from May 1984 to April 1985 by Marvel Comics. From July 1985 to March 1986, a sequel, Secret Wars II, was published.

The series was conceived by Marvel Comics\&#039; Editor-in-chief Jim Shooter and primarily pencilled by Mike Zeck.

This is a request from the forum. Request was only for Secret Wars II, but I decided to do both I and II to make it a more complete post. You can also find these among various chronologies already uploaded. But if you want only Secret Wars then this is for you. Enjoy and Seed.
